data.description:
Traditional 3-2-1 property only minutes from EpicCentral! This home has a large living area perfect for family gatherings with french doors leading to concrete patio area. Good size Master bedroom with walk in closet, sink vanity with make-up area. Good size backyard with nice size side yard. Home is located in a cul de sac street, so no thru traffic. Perfect for first time homebuyers!
Foundation work done with transferable warranty and roof is less than 2years old!
